Class LocationUpdateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • DeviceData
      • com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.data.LocationUpdate
        • com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.event.LocationUpdateEvent

  • public class LocationUpdateEvent
extends LocationUpdate
    This event is posted via the EventBus. Register on the EventBus for this event type to see the data that ExactTarget sends to their servers.

    Sent after the user's current location has been successfully sent to ExactTarget.
